{"word":"G2026 - ἐποικοδομέω - epoikodoméō - ep-oy-kod-om-eh'-o - Build thereon","slug":"G2026","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἐποικοδομέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>epoikodoméō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>ep-oy-kod-om-eh'-o"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Build thereon"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03B5;&#x0313;&#x03C0;&#x03BF;&#x03B9;&#x03BA;&#x03BF;&#x03B4;&#x03BF;&#x03BC;&#x03B5;&#x0301;&#x03C9; - epoikodomeo&#x0304;</b> - <i>ep-oy-kod-om-eh'-o</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/G1909\">G1909</a> and <a href=\"#/G3618\">G3618</a>; to <i>build upon</i>, that is, (figuratively) to <i>rear up:</i> - build thereon (thereupon, on, upon)."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G2731\">G2731</a>, <a href=\"#/G2732\">G2732</a>, <a href=\"#/G2733\">G2733</a>, <a href=\"#/G3609\">G3609</a>, <a href=\"#/G3611\">G3611</a>, <a href=\"#/G3613\">G3613</a>, <a href=\"#/G3614\">G3614</a>, <a href=\"#/G3615\">G3615</a>, <a href=\"#/G3616\">G3616</a>, <a href=\"#/G3617\">G3617</a>, <a href=\"#/G3618\">G3618</a>, <a href=\"#/G3619\">G3619</a>, <a href=\"#/G3620\">G3620</a>, <a href=\"#/G3621\">G3621</a>, <a href=\"#/G3622\">G3622</a>, <a href=\"#/G3623\">G3623</a>, <a href=\"#/G3624\">G3624</a>, <a href=\"#/G4925\">G4925</a>"}]}